description: This data reports average arrival delay and sources of delay for non-stop flights going into major airports in the U.S.  (First Quarter 2007). The data summarizes flights for 19 carriers - i.e., those carriers that have at least 1% of total domestic passenger revenue.The source of the data is the BTS Airline On-Time Performance and Causes of Flight Delay database.
